INSERT INTO `vacations` VALUES (12,'test555','test1000','2023-03-25','2023-03-30',994,'[object FileList]'),(242,'London, England','London is one of the world\'s most iconic cities, renowned for its rich history, iconic landmarks such as Big Ben and Buckingham Palace, and its bustling streets filled with vibrant culture and entertainment.','2023-03-25','2023-03-29',1200,'https://www.history.com/.image/ar_1:1%2Cc_fill%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_1200/MTYyNDg1MjE3MTI1Mjc5Mzk4/topic-london-gettyimages-760251843-promo.jpg'),(243,'Berlin, Germany','Berlin is a city steeped in history, from its role as the capital of the Third Reich to its role in the Cold War and the fall of the Berlin Wall. Today, it\'s a thriving hub of culture and creativity, with a thriving arts and music scene.','2023-03-15','2023-03-20',900,'https://s7g10.scene7.com/is/image/stena/20150820_berlin-brandenburg-gate:16-9?ts=1656740748478&dpr=off'),(245,'Prague, Czech Republic','	Prague is a city steeped in history, with a rich cultural heritage, stunning Gothic and Renaissance architecture, and famous for its picturesque bridges over the Vltava River. It\'s also renowned for its vibrant nightlife and delicious cuisine','2023-03-18','2023-03-22',700,'https://a.cdn-hotels.com/gdcs/production76/d1135/21203dce-feeb-40f3-8c93-fc1a98f7549a.jpg'),(246,'Budapest, Hungary','	Budapest is a city of two halves, with the hilly Buda district on one side of the river and the flat Pest district on the other. It\'s famous for its thermal baths, stunning architecture and its rich cultural heritage.','2023-03-11','2023-04-17',800,'https://www.meininger-hotels.com/blog/app/uploads/2021/05/shutterstock_768128938-min-scaled.jpg'),(248,'Santorini, Greece','Santorini is a stunning Greek island, famous for its white-washed buildings, stunning sunsets and beautiful beaches. It\'s also a hub of culture, with numerous ancient ruins and stunning churches.','2023-03-15','2023-03-20',900,'https://lp-cms-production.imgix.net/2021-05/shutterstockRF_1563449509.jpg?auto=format&q=75&w=3840'),(252,'Sri Lanka','	Sri Lanka is a tropical paradise that offers visitors the chance to immerse themselves in rich history, culture and natural beauty. With its stunning temples, ancient ruins and lush vegetation, it\'s a true gem of the Indian Ocean that should not be misse...','2023-07-01','2023-07-05',1300,'https://dynamic-media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/0d/f9/8f/0a/one-of-the-best-travel.jpg?w=700&h=-1&s=1'),(253,'New York, USA','Explore the city that never sleeps with its towering skyscrapers, world-famous museums, and diverse neighborhoods. Take a stroll through Central Park, catch a Broadway show, or indulge in some of the best food and shopping in the world. With endless things to see and do, New York is a must-visit destination for any traveler.','2023-06-01','2023-06-07',2000,'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRV7bYmfqYyonSzQioyZz4pP9Lgsfdkz4Rk6g&usqp=CAU'),(254,'Bali, Indonesia','Experience the ultimate island getaway in Bali, Indonesia. Relax on stunning beaches, explore lush forests and rice paddies, and immerse yourself in the local culture with visits to temples and traditional markets. Indulge in delicious local cuisine and rejuvenate with yoga and spa treatments. Bali offers the perfect blend of relaxation and adventure for your dream vacation.','2023-07-10','2023-07-17',2500,'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRo6EHoiR0vLVrbEtRIgxuX07dPJuoK63Y_0g&usqp=CAU'),(255,'Tokyo, Japan','Tokyo is a vibrant city that offers visitors a unique experience of traditional and modern Japanese culture. The city is a hub of innovation, technology, and entertainment, with towering skyscrapers and neon lights that illuminate the streets at night. At the same time, Tokyo also preserves its rich cultural heritage with temples, shrines, and traditional gardens that offer a glimpse into Japan\'s ancient past.','2023-09-01','2023-09-08',3000,'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTzlsMmDaRoiZUakIMj7vunE3LtC6tULmXkTw&usqp=CAU'),(256,'Dubai, UAE','shopping malls, and endless entertainment options. Located in the United Arab Emirates, Dubai is a popular destination for travelers seeking a luxurious escape.','2023-10-01','2023-10-07',3500,'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSKMigaogsdSFZLKkiDJj7WS2yySUmvz95sqg&usqp=CAU'),(257,'Amalfi Coast, Italy','The Amalfi Coast in Italy is known for its breathtaking views, charming towns, and scenic drives. Indulge in the delicious Italian cuisine and local wines while taking in the beauty of the rugged coastline and turquoise waters of the Tyrrhenian Sea. Explore the picturesque towns of Positano, Amalfi, and Ravello, each with its own unique character and charm. Admire the colorful houses perched on cliffs overlooking the sea, and wander the narrow streets lined with shops and cafes. ','2023-11-01','2023-11-07',2800,'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQuG57FuAr2iqFQyHCkCa4Vh8WA79SPUMSr-A&usqp=CAU'),(258,'Rio de Janeiro, Brazil','Rio de Janeiro, Brazil is a vibrant and lively destination that is famous for its samba music, colorful culture, and breathtaking scenery. The city is home to iconic landmarks such as the Christ the Redeemer statue and Sugarloaf Mountain. Visitors can enjoy a variety of activities including sunbathing on Copacabana Beach, exploring the Tijuca Forest, and indulging in traditional Brazilian cuisine. Rio de Janeiro is also famous for its Carnival, a week-long celebration of music, dance, and culture that is unlike any other in the world. Whether you\'re looking for adventure, relaxation, or a taste of Brazilian culture, Rio de Janeiro has something for everyone.','2023-12-01','2023-12-07',2200,'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTd6meg4bV8FMdtQw39Yk2PCc8HEO1Hq0Qtng&usqp=CAU'),(259,'Kruger National Park, South Africa','Kruger National Park is one of the largest game reserves in Africa, spanning over 7,500 square miles in northeastern South Africa. It is home to a vast array of wildlife, including the famous \"Big Five\": lions, leopards, elephants, rhinos, and buffalos. Visitors can go on a safari adventure and see these majestic animals up close in their natural habitats. The park also offers breathtaking landscapes and diverse ecosystems, making it a nature lover\'s paradise.','2023-01-15','2023-01-22',4000,'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTOuA6h2NlwMSzVrWtNeexV5AINnR8joIeQig&usqp=CAU'),(260,'Phuket, Thailand','Phuket is one of the most popular tourist destinations in Thailand, known for its stunning beaches and crystal clear waters. This tropical island is located in the Andaman Sea and offers a range of activities for visitors to unwind and relax. Some of the most popular activities include swimming, sunbathing, snorkeling, and diving. In addition to its natural beauty, Phuket is also known for its vibrant nightlife, delicious cuisine, and rich culture. ','2023-02-01','2023-02-07',2200,'https://www.cunard.com/content/dam/cunard/inventory-assets/ports/PHU/PHU.jpg'),(261,'Barcelona, Spain','Barcelona is a vibrant and cosmopolitan city located on the northeastern coast of Spain. It\'s famous for its stunning architecture, which includes works by the renowned architect Antoni Gaudi, such as the iconic Sagrada Familia church and Park Guell. Barcelona is also known for its bustling street life, with lively neighborhoods such as Las Ramblas and the Gothic Quarter. Visitors can enjoy world-class dining and shopping, as well as an exciting nightlife scene. ','2023-03-01','2023-03-07',1800,'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTpri3D_YYYAF2Bz2Bg0pLhCuYWJeqBjyoyUw&usqp=CAU'),(262,'Hawaii, USA','Hawaii is a stunning archipelago in the Pacific Ocean, famous for its stunning beaches, vibrant culture and stunning natural scenery. It\'s also a hub of history and culture, with numerous ancient ruins and beautiful temples.','2023-04-01','2023-04-07',2500,'https://www.touristsecrets.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/feature-1.jpg'),(263,'Tuscany, Italy','Experience the beauty and charm of the Tuscan countryside, with its rolling hills, vineyards, and historic towns. Indulge in the delicious flavors of Italian cuisine, from freshly made pasta to world-renowned wines. Take in the stunning architecture and art of Florence, Siena, and other nearby cities. Whether you\'re looking for a romantic getaway or a relaxing escape, Tuscany is the perfect destination for a truly unforgettable vacation.','2023-05-01','2023-05-07',2800,'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRv9jHlC0p6Eu7Vvf9W8ZlZHU9mdu-kssy2Sg&usqp=CAU'),(264,'Cape Town, South Africa','Cape Town, South Africa is a destination that offers a perfect blend of natural beauty and urban charm. With its stunning coastline and iconic landmarks, such as Table Mountain and Robben Island, Cape Town is a must-visit for any traveler. Explore the city\'s rich history and culture by visiting the museums and historical sites, or indulge in the local cuisine and wine in the nearby winelands. Take a trip to the top of Table Mountain for panoramic views of the city and surrounding landscapes, or spend a day relaxing on the beautiful beaches. ','2023-06-01','2023-06-07',3000,'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSJln2WRHLTjhwzI-mVG8trgH3SzbiagB1uKw&usqp=CAU'),(265,'israel','test','2023-03-25','2023-03-30',2222,'undefined');
